T1  - A Note on the Equilibrium Existence Problem in Discontinuous Games
AU  - Barelli, Paulo
AU  - Meneghel, Idione
Y1  - 2013/03/01
PY  - 2013
DA  - 2013/03/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.3982/ECTA9125
